      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  ambulatory patient with cirrhosis

          -  baseline Cr &lt;2

          -  ability to complete psychometric testing

          -  refractory ascites

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Cr &gt;2

          -  history of Gastrointestinal bleed

          -  history of infection

          -  history of renal failure
      </textblock>
